quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,Meunyo Meusayang le Kamoe keu jih j Meupeuleupah jih dum han le sosah Teuntee jimeuʻen lam darohaka Hana le reuda jipeubuet salah
  23,76,Ka lheueh Kamoe bri roe azeueb keu jih Han cit jitem jih turot peurintah Han jitem teukui keudeh keu Po jih
  23,77,Meubri treuk keu jih azeueb that leupah Meujeuet treuk jih nyan dum putoh asa ‘Oh pinto seksa ka Kamoe peuhah
  23,78,Tuhan nyang peujeuet geulunyueng mata Ngon ate gata carong ngon ceudah Tapi nit gata nyang tatem chukor
  23,79,Neubri gata le di bumoe Allah Meuaneuk cucoteuh dum di bumoe Meusapat dudoe teuma bak Allah
  23,80,Tuhan peuhudep Tuhan peumate Malam teuka le uroe pih leupah Malam ngon uroe cit meungkleh sabe Hankeuh tapike ngon akai ceudah
  23,81,Tapi kheunjih sa ngon ureueng jameun Saban ngon jih kheun hana meuubah
  23,82,Jikheun peue keubit ‘oh mate tanyoe Geubangket tanyoe teuma geupeugah p *Oh jeuet keu tanoh teuh tinggai tuleueng Geubangket teuh lom mustahe leupah
  23,83,Keubit geutanyoe ngon du-du tanyoe Geujanji meunoe dilee ka sudah Atranyoe dongeng ureueng nyang dilee Bandum meuteuntee haba beurakah
  23,84,Takheun soe nyang po bumoe ngon asoe Bandum sinaroe tacuba peugah Meunyo tateupeue takheun soe po jih
  23,85,Teuntee seuotjih nyang po nyan Allah Takheun boh pakon cit han taingat
  23,86,Takheun po langet soe lom ci peugah Po langet tujoh po ‘arasy raya
  23,87,Jiseuot lanja po jih nyan Allah Takheun boh pakon han tatakwa
  23,88,Takheun soe raja lom taci peugah Nyang po keurajeuen seugala rupa Nyang ek neubela soe-soe nyang sosah Beurangsoe laen han ek jibela Meunyo neuseksa soe nyan ci peugah Meunyo tateupeue takheun soe dih nyan
  23,89,Teuntee jikheun nyan cit sidroe Allah Takheun peue cit ek gata jitaki
  23,90,Tapi ka Meubri keu jih dum sudah Atra nyang beuna ka lheueh Kamoe bri Droe jih nyang taki sulet that leupah
  23,91,Hana aneuk-Neuh sagai di Tuhan Tan laen tuhan sajan ngon Allah Sabab meunyo na tuhan nyang laen r Makhluk laen geupeujeuet sudah Meuseunoh-seunoh peugot atra droe 3 Ka keuh rayek droe bandum geupeugah Maha Suci that Allah lagee nyan
  23,92,Nyang keubit Tuhan cit sidroe Allah Nyang han deuh taeu got nyang deuh taeu Bandum deuh Neueu meunyo le Allah Bandum deuh Neueu Maha manyang that Nibak charikat lagee jih peugah
  23,93,Takheun Tuhanku meunyo Neumeung bri Peue nyang Neujanji Neumeung peuleumah Neumeung peukalon atra nyan bak lon
  23,94,Tuhanku bek lon roh lam beurakah Bek roh lon dalam kaom nyang lalem
  23,95,Meunyo Kamoe tem ek Meupeuleumah Ek Meupeukalon dum nyan bak gata
  23,96,Teuma digata beugot tapapah Tatulak ngon got buet nyang brok jih nyan Kamoe teupeue nyan peue nyang jipeugah
  23,97,Takheun Tuhanku Neupeulindong lon Nibak s‘ah chetan jiyue buet salah
  23,98,Neupeulindong lon wahe Tuhanku Bek jipeukaru bak lon jilangkah
  23,99,Teuma awak nyan ‘oh teuka mawot Han ek le meumot jikheun treuk bagah Tuhanku Neubri lon woe u donya
  23,100,Lon peubuet teuma amai jroh leupah Amai nyang shaleh nyang tinggai dilee Jinoe meuteuntee han le lon keubah Tapi atra nyan narit jih mantong Di likot jih dong padang that luah Sampoe geubangket jih han troh teuka
  23,101,‘Oh Sangkai kala pih geuyup sudah Uroe nyan han le geutanyong bangsa Han le chedara nyang meugah-meugah Han jeuet teumanyong le bak uroe nyan
  23,102,Nyang brat timbangan nyan nyang meutuah Nyankeuh ureueng nyan nyang meubahgia
  23,103,Nyang phui ceulaka rugoe sileupah Jipeurugoe droe roh lam nuraka Keukai jeuep masa lam apui mirah
  23,104,Jisama muža jitot le apui Meugasui-gasui hanco ngon patah b i
  23,105,Kon ka geubaca dilee ayat Lon Keu gata bandum sulet tapeugah
  23,106,Kheun treuk awak nyan hai Tuhan kamoe Jigiduek kamoe le buet nyang salah £ Kakeuh meunang jih u ateueh kamoe Jeuet treuk dum kamoe sisat sileupah
  23,107,Neubri meuteubiet nibak teumpat nyoe Hai Tuhan kamoe saket that leupah Meunyo kamoe woe buet lagee dilee H Nyan ka meuteuntee kamoe nyang salah Kamoe nyang lalem droe meuelanya
  23,108,Neukheun bah hinakeuh sinan dikah Beujrakeuh sinan mangat karasa Bek le meuhaba ngon Lon nyoe dikah
  23,109,Saboh jamaʻah nibak hamba Lon Ureueng nyan geukheun wahe ya Allah Wahe Po kamoe kamoe meuiman Neuampon teuma kamoe ka salah Droe-Neuh sineujroh ureueng geumaseh Kamoe Neugaseh wahe ya Allah
  23,110,Kaulok-ulok ureueng nyan bandum Hingga jeuet keu Lon tuwokeuh dikah f Bandumkeuh tuwo kaingat keu Lon Dawok kapeukhem ureueng nyan dikah
  23,111,Uroe nyoe gopnyan nyang meubahgia k Sabab geusaba jinoe Lon balah
  23,112,Neukheun padum thon keuh dalam bumoe
  23,113,Sang-sang siuroe jiseuot bagah Meukon siuroe sang sikhan uroe Tatanyong keudroe bak ureueng ceudah Keudeh bak ureueng nyang jeuet meubileueng
  23,114,Sideh kah geukheun rijang sileupah Meunyo kateupeue sideh kah tinggai Cit siat sagai leupah that bagah
  23,115,Peue bak tasangka Meupeujeuet gata Cit sia-sia hana phaedah p Hana geupeuwoe gata le bak Lon
  23,116,Maha Suci Lon Raja nyang meugah Raja nyang beuna nyang mat keurajeuen Kon laen tuhan meulengkan Allah Allahkeuh nyang Po ‘arasy mulia
  23,117,Soe nyang tapuja meunyo kon Allah Beurangsoe puja tuhan nyang laen Jikheun na laen sajan ngon Allah Hana meudali nyang jipeugah nyan Neukira dum nyan teuma le Allah Tuhan nyang Po jih peugot keunira Hana bahgia si kaphe jadah
  23,118,Takheun Tuhanku beu-Neupeuampon Neugaseh keu lon ureueng nyang salah Droe-Neuh sineujroh ureueng geumaseh Bandum Neugaseh wahe ya Allah AN-NUR (CAHAYA) s Ngon nama Allah lon peuphon surat Tuhan Hadharat nyang Maha Murah Tuhanku Sidroe geumaseh that-that Donya akhirat rahmat Neulimpah